00:05:47.690 --> 00:05:50.330
want to know which is the right
retailer to purchase

00:05:50.330 --> 00:05:50.920
this product.

00:05:50.920 --> 00:05:52.850
So that's where we show you that
information and then we

00:05:52.850 --> 00:05:54.650
show you the price and
other attributes.

00:05:54.650 --> 00:05:56.310
So that's where the next

00:05:56.310 --> 00:06:00.130
evolution in Google's shopping.

