00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:58.630
So we have an API called Search
API for Shopping, which

00:10:58.630 --> 00:11:00.740
allows you to take a lot of
innovations that are happening

00:11:00.740 --> 00:11:02.440
on Google to power
the e-commerce

00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:04.140
experience on your website.

00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:08.280
And also, that API allows you to
monetize the data inventory

00:11:08.280 --> 00:11:09.880
feed here at Google.

00:11:09.880 --> 00:11:13.600
So you can be a publisher,
what we call, at Google,

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:14.080
Affiliate Networks.

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:17.540
So you can be an affiliate on
the Google Affiliate Network

00:11:17.540 --> 00:11:19.700
and publish some of
these items. And

00:11:19.700 --> 00:11:20.790
this applies to anybody.

00:11:20.790 --> 00:11:22.090
You don't need to
be a retailer.

00:11:22.090 --> 00:11:25.180
If you're a website owner,
blogger, or publisher, you can

00:11:25.180 --> 00:11:28.090
leverage that API to monetize
your website better.

00:11:28.090 --> 00:11:30.530
So we're going to talk about
both of these APIs in a lot

00:11:30.530 --> 00:11:34.300
