Well, if we have a specific
product operation, if you want

00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:10.150
to update the information,
if you want to delete the

00:21:10.150 --> 00:21:14.610
information, this is the
endpoint we'd use.

00:21:14.610 --> 00:21:20.240
So what we have online, is
it's an [? arguable ?]

00:21:20.240 --> 00:21:23.320
code site, is an interactive
