up with the API.

00:21:30.040 --> 00:21:32.940
What it allows you to do is,
enter your values, either in a

00:21:32.940 --> 00:21:35.560
form, or as raw XML.

00:21:35.560 --> 00:21:38.920
You make the request and, I
don't know if you can see with

